INSERT INTO `x2_questions` VALUES (1,1,'How many bytes does a IPv6 address contain?',0,'','','A.16\nB.32\nC.64\nD.128',4,'A','128bits, 16bytes。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(2,2,'Except the SLAAC(stateless address autoconfiguration), which of following method can set IPv6 addresses for a node?',0,'','','A.Manual\nB.DHCPv6\nC.ICMPv6',3,'AB','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(3,2,'Compares with IPv4, which of following are new characteristics of IPv6?',0,'','','A.Extend header makes more flexible and efficient\nB.Multicast replacing broadcast\nC.Address migration mechanism\nD.More fields than IPv4 header',4,'ABC','IPv6包头中的字段少于IPv4，但提供的功能更加灵活实用。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(4,1,'Which of following mechanism is not needed by IPv6 network？',0,'','','A.Address advertised\nB.Address resolution\nC.Address translation\nD.Duplicate Address Detection',4,'C','NAT技术设计的初衷是为了节约IPv4中的公网地址空间。IPv6大量的可用地址空间，决定了不再需要NAT技术。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(5,2,'What are differences between IPv6 and IPv4 header?',0,'','','A.More 20 bytes length than IPv4 header\nB.Less fields than IPv4 header\nC.IPv6 header support network checksum\nD.Extend header in IPv6 header replacing Option in IPv4 header',4,'ABD','IPv6包头中不再提供网络层校验功能，因为二层和四层都有相应的校验功能。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(6,2,'What are the reasons for extend header improving IPv6 forwarding efficiency?',0,'','','A.extend header is tailer of IPv6 header\nB.extend header is stackable\nC.only aim needs to decapsulate extend header normally\nD.transport router needn\'t to detect extend header normally',4,'CD','扩展包头类似于MPLS的多层标签，通常情况下只有接收端才需要查看扩展包头的内容，而路径上的转发路由器只需要查看前面的IPv6包头内容即可完成转发内容。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(7,2,'Which of following fields dispeared in IPv6 header?',0,'','','A.Header length\nB.Identification\nC.Flags\nD.Fragment Offset\nE.Header checksum\nF.Options\nG.Padding',7,'ABCDEFG','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(8,1,'Which is new field in IPv6 header(not include renamed)?',0,'','','A.Traffic Class\nB.Flow Label\nD.Next Header\nE.Hop Limit',5,'B','以下是由IPv4变化而来的字段：\nTOS-&gt;Traffic Class\nTotal Length-&gt;Payload Length\nProtocol-&gt;Next Header\nTTL-&gt;Hop Limit','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(9,1,'Which header does not have checksum?',0,'','','A.Link Layer Header\nB.IPv6 Header\nC.TCP Header\nD.UDP Header',4,'B','IPv6包头取消校验字段；UDP包头的校验功能在IPv4中为可选，到了IPv6中改为强制。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(10,2,'Which of following IS a type of IPv6 address?',0,'','','A.Unicast\nB.Anycast\nC.Multicast\nD.Broadcast',4,'ABC','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(11,2,'Which are properly descriptions of Link-local address?',0,'','','A.scope of local link\nB.can be used to forward packet\nC.may duplicate on several interfaces in one node\nD.cannot config manually',4,'AC','Link-Local地址不能转发数据，只能用于本链路通信,并且支持手动配置。Link-local地址是基于接口的MAC地址自动生成的，且没有MAC地址的接口会借用以太网接口的MAC地址用于自动生成，所以同一台站点上的不同接口，可能会出现地址重复的现象。在使用Link-local地址时，系统会提示选择哪个接口通信。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(12,3,'当以太网帧头的type字段为0x86DD，说明网络层使用了IPv6协议。',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(13,1,'以太网地址ca03.1bd8.0008，对应的EUI-64接口标识是多少？',0,'','','A.::C803:1BFF:FED8:8\nB.::FF:FE:CA03:1BD8:8',2,'A','MAC地址转换为EUI-64地址的方法为：中间加&quot;FFFE&quot;,7bit置1。例如ca03.1bd8.0008，就转换为ca03:1bff:fed8:0008，再修改第7bit为1，表示该地址全球唯一，即ca08:1bff:fed8:8。加上前面的网段结果就是2001::ca03:1bff:fed8:8','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"7\";s:5:\"knows\";s:18:\"IPv6 Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(14,2,'IPv6中用什么方式解决MTU相关问题？',0,'','','A.路径中的转发路由器根据IPv6包头中的Payload Length与出接口MTU比较，超过则分片传输\nB.采用PMTU方式得到路径最小MTU\nC.始发节点根据路径最小MTU进行分片\nD.接收节点根据IPv6包头中的identifier进行分片重组',4,'BC','IPv6中，中间转发节点已经不再负责分配工作。始发节点通过PMTU来获取路径最小MTU，自行分片发出。只有在接收节点上，根据IPv6包头扩展头信息来进行重组。IPv6包头中取消了identifier字段，分片信息被放置在专门的fragment extend header中存储。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"3\";s:5:\"knows\";s:19:\"IPv6 Basic Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(15,3,'ICMPv6的Router Advertisement消息中包含IPv6 Prefix, Lifetime, Default Router\n和Flag option这些字段。',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(16,2,'如何实现无状态自动配置(SLAAC)？',0,'','','A.DHCP服务器自动下发地址\nB.路由器自动下发地址段\nC.客户端以接收到的信息和自身信息作为地址',3,'BC','路由器下发IPv6 Prefix，客户端再用自身Link-local地址与Prefix进行组合生成接口的IPv6 Global地址。路由器下发的prefix必须是IPv6地址的前64bits，客户端接到prefix后用eui-64方法补齐后64bits。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(17,2,'以下哪些属于IPv6地址中的组播地址？',0,'','','A.FF02::1\nB.FF02::2\nC.FF02::1:FFXX:XXXX',3,'ABC','指定节点的组播地址映射方式是单播地址的后24bits复制到组播地址的最后24bits。例如2001:410:0:1:0:0:0:45FF\n对应的节点组播地址是FF02::1:FF00:45FF','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(18,2,'以下哪些是IPv6扩展ACL中的隐式规则？',0,'','','A.permit icmp any any nd-ns\nB.permit icmp any any nd-na\nC.permit icmp any any\nD.deny ipv6 any any',4,'ABD','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"5\";s:5:\"knows\";s:13:\"IPv6 Security\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(19,2,'以下哪些网络管理工具可以在IPv6环境中使用？',0,'','','A.ping\nB.traceroute\nC.telnet\nD.ssh\nE.tftp',5,'ABCDE','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"7\";s:5:\"knows\";s:18:\"IPv6 Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(20,1,'在Cisco IOS中，要配置IPv6环境，需要提前开启的命令有？',0,'','','A.ipv6 unicast-routing\nB.ipv6 enable\nC.ipv6 cef\nD.ipv6 address autoconfig',4,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"7\";s:5:\"knows\";s:18:\"IPv6 Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(21,2,'以下哪些属于BGP4+的新增特性？',0,'','','A.NEXT_HOP属性可以携带IPv6地址\nB.NEXT_HOP属性可以同时携带IPv6 Global和Link-Local地址\nC.NLRI字段可以携带IPv6路由前缀\nD.可以忽略AS-Path属性的比较',4,'ABC','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(22,1,'RIPng协议的IPv6组播地址是什么？',0,'','','A.224.0.0.9\nB.FF02::9\nC.FF01::9\nD.FF02::2',4,'B','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(23,2,'下列哪项属于ISIS协议为IPv6新增的TLV字段？',0,'','','A.IPv6 reachability\nB.IPv6 interface address\nC.IPv6 NIS\nD.IPv6 LSP',4,'AB','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(24,1,'在Cisco IOS中，如何启用接口的OSPFv3进程？',0,'','','A.router ospf process-id\nB.network subnet wildmask area area-id\nC.ipv6 ospf process-id area area-id',3,'D','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(25,1,'当IPv6报文被封装到IPv4报文内部时，IPv4包头的Protocol字段使用什么值来表示这种封装？',0,'','','A.6\nB.41\nC.4',3,'B','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(26,2,'哪种场景可以使用IPv4隧道封装IPv6技术？',0,'','','A.Host to Host\nB.Router to Host\nC.Router to Router',3,'ABC','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(27,2,'下列哪些技术可用于IPv4与IPv6的融合隧道技术？',0,'','','A.6to4\nB.GRE\nC.L2TP\nD.MPLS',4,'AB',