3 area ID combination assigns interfaces to OSPFv3 areas.\nB. In router configuration mode, the network wildcard area ID combination assigns networks to OSPFv3 areas.\nC. In interface configuration mode, the IPv6 OSPF process area ID combination assigns interfaces to OSPFv3 areas.\nD. In router configuration mode, the IPv6 OSPF interface area ID combination assigns interfaces to OSPFv3 areas.',4,'C','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(83,3,'NAT-PT设备通常处于纯IPv4网络和纯IPv6网络的交界处。',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(84,1,'During the IPv6 autoconfiguration, what does the device append to the 64-bit prefix that it receives from the router to create its IPv6 address?',0,'','','A. a pseudorandom generated number\nB. its locally configured IPv4 address\nC. its interface ID',3,'C','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"knows\";s:41:\"Addressing Architecture and Configuration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(85,2,'Which is characteristic of IPv6?',0,'','','A. An IPv6 address is 128 bits long.\nB. An IPv6 header is 40 bits long.\nC. An IPv6 header descripts upper protocol type.\nD. An IPv6 header contains the header checksum field.',4,'AC','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"1\";s:5:\"knows\";s:12:\"IPv6 Concept\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(86,2,'&lt;p&gt;When an IPv6 enabled host boots, it sends a router solicitation (RS) message. An IPv6 router responds with a router advertisement (RA). Which two items are contained in the RA?&lt;/p&gt;',0,'','','&lt;p&gt;A.IPv6 address for the host B.lifetime of the prefix C.prefixes for the link D.keepalive timers&lt;/p&gt;',4,'BC','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"3\";s:5:\"knows\";s:19:\"IPv6 Basic Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(87,3,'After you accomplish clear ipv6 ospf process command, OSPF database will be repopulated and SP