ling\nC. NAT-PT',3,'C','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(159,3,'Tunnel broker establishes a tunnel with users.',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'B','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(160,2,'What is 6RD?',0,'','','A. IPv6 Rapid Development\nB.Similar with 6to4, but not use 2002:: /16 prefix\nC. The length of 6RD prefix is stable',3,'AB','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(161,3,'In 6RD scene includes 6RD CE and 6RD BR.',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(162,3,'ISATAP tunneling uses address translation mechanism.',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'B','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(163,3,'In IPv6, tunneling mechanism means encapsulating IPv6 packets inside IPv4 packets to carry IPv6 packets over IPv4 network infrastructures.',0,'','','A.√\nB.×',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"6\";s:5:\"knows\";s:25:\"IPv4 and IPv6 Integration\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(164,1,'Three bank employees are using the corporate network. The first employee uses a web browser to view a company web page in order to read some announcements. The second employee accesses the corporate database to perform some financial transactions. The third employee participates in an important live audio conference with other corporate managers in branch offices. If QoS is implemented on this network, what will be the priorities from highest to lowest of the different data types?',0,'','','A. audio conference, financial transactions, web page\nB. audio conference, web page, financial transactions\nC. web page, financial transactions, audio conference\nD. financial transactions, web page, audio conference',4,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"3\";s:5:\"knows\";s:19:\"IPv6 Basic Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(165,2,'下列支持IPv4的路由协议，哪些协议扩展到支持IPv6会更容易，改动相对较少？',0,'','','A.RIP\nB.IS-IS\nC.OSPF\nD.BGP',4,'BD','ISIS与BGP都属于TLV结构设计，相对于OSPF这种固定结构设计的路由协议，在对协议进行功能扩展的时候更加容易，改动更少。另外ISIS是基于链路层的协议，用于IP路由时，协议数据包的传输依赖更少，所以更加容易扩展到IPv6.','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(166,2,'在MPBGP中，如果用IPv4地址建立peer，那么这一对peer之间可以传输以下哪些路由信息？',0,'','','A.IPv4 unicast\nB.IPv6 unicast\nC.VPNv4 unicast\nD.IPv4 multicast',4,'ABCD','MPBGP中，建立peer的地址类型与所传输的路由信息类型没有绝对的关联关系，建立peer的地址只用来建立TCP通道，在这个通道的封装下，各种类型的路由信息都在UPDATE消息中进行传播。需要注意的是应该将UPDATE message中的NEXT_HOP信息修改为对应的地址类型。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,3),(167,1,'OSPFv3中，采用哪种地址作为router-id？',0,'','','A.IPv4\nB.IPv6',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(168,1,'BGP4+中，采用哪种地址作为router-id？',0,'','','A.IPv4\nB.IPv6',2,'A','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(169,2,'MPBGP中，可以用哪种地址建立IPv6 BGP邻居？',0,'','','A.Global address\nB.Link-local address\nC.Anycast address',3,'AB','在AS边界，属于不同管理体制下的两台路由器通常不方便配置同一AS的global address, 所以IPv6 eBGP邻居通常使用link-local地址建立邻居。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,2),(170,1,'RIPng的最大跳数限制是多少？',0,'','','A.15\nB.255\nC.unlimited',3,'A','RIPng继承了RIP的最大跳数限制，最大跳数为15跳，16跳被认为不可达。','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',1418202939,1,'',0,0,1),(171,2,'RIPng的协议报文是如何传递的？',0,'','','A.以link-local为源地址\nB.以global地址为源地址\nC.以组播地址FF02::9为目的地址\nD.以UDP521为目的端口',4,'ACD','','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:7:\"knowsid\";s:1:\"4\";s:5:\"knows\";s:21:\"IPv6 Routing Protocal\";}}',141820293